#! Capabilities — the app's ENTIRE privileged surface, in one auditable place. Every grant
#! lives here; feature slices import this module and attenuate to just the one capability
#! they need (via using). The program budget bounds total cost across all features.
#! @requires settle, refund — the irreversible payment effects
grant settle cost 10 irreversible confidence 70
grant refund cost 8 irreversible confidence 70
budget 100
